Package sk.musicstore.services

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DrumService
    The class controls the logic of queries to the drums table in the database.
    GuitarService
    The class controls the logic of queries to the guitars table in the database.
    OrderService
    The class controls the logic of queries to the order user table and order guitar, order drum, order synthesizer in the database.
    ProductService
    Class for returning a complete list of products from the database
    SessionUtils
    Helper class for working with the session.
    SynthesizerService
    The class controls the logic of queries to the synthesizers table in the database.
    UserService
